{"tid":835959,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★iOS12新BUG：屏幕色彩失真，信號變差","createTime":"2018-09-25T10:08:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-25T10:18:40.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ac9e123263173313b2b688b617e8e1a6b135a5a8","tid":835959,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T10:08:14.000Z","msg":"根據福布斯報導，部分iPhone X的使用者在將系統升級至iOS12之後，發現iPhone X的OLED屏幕在顏色對比度及色彩平衡上出現了偏差，iPhone X在iOS12的屏幕顯示效果遠不及iOS11。<br />\n<br />\n屏幕色彩問題在iOS12的測試版中就出現過，用戶也反饋過該問題，不過蘋果至今沒有修復BUG。<br />\n<br />\n此外今天還出現了許多用戶吐槽iPhone XS系列新機的LTE及Wi-Fi信號出現了問題。用戶表示在4G網絡時，信號就變得很差，由於許多投訴者都來自於自運營商Verizon的用戶，且運營商AT&amp;T普遍表示信號比之前還好，所以暫時不能確定是手機問題還是運營商問題。<br />\n<br />\n還有一部分iPhone XS的用戶認為該問題可能與新機使用了高通或英特爾調製解調器有關。<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，iPhone XS及iPhone XS Max的Wi-Fi似乎也出現了不好的現象。據MacRumors論壇用戶反應，新iPhone總是喜歡連接2.4GHZ頻段的Wi-Fi信號，而不是5GHz，2.4GHZ的Wi-Fi信號總是發生網絡擁堵導致使用體驗下降。<br />\n<br />\n目前不確定LTE的信號問題是系統問題還是硬件問題，但是Wi-Fi問題似乎可以通過系統更新來解決，畢竟5GHz網絡與2.4GHz頻段，iPhone XS及iPhone XS Max都是支持的。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ithome.com/0/385/181.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com%2F0%2F385%2F181.htm&d=V6eIsC6tCqaMTQGh%2Fab2vjACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=6ad62d32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ithome.com/0/385/181.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8aa94082eba602aee5cc23a5c31c4d803a3239e2","tid":835959,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T10:08:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"167635f1aee754bbd62efbe86c40b604965a92d3","tid":835959,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T10:09:06.000Z","msg":"apple rip"},{"pid":"fa7679195a5b1f837a1846481a4345731d32a546","tid":835959,"uid":37136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T10:16:23.000Z","msg":"iPhone X series rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"722f60dd2f7faeb43327424fad93a6369d3e8150","tid":835959,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T10:17:35.000Z","msg":"係時候換機啦"},{"pid":"e9bf0147f3512f6e1b54b9d87bc838934fc7e2a3","tid":835959,"uid":24660,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T10:17:54.000Z","msg":"樓豬係打手"},{"pid":"be8eef97edf44e588158878f807fd8027d0921ba","tid":835959,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T10:18:40.000Z","msg":"聽得IOS多Android 有咩bug?"}]}